text: David George "Dave" Reichert (; born August 29, 1950) is an American politician. He was the U.S. Representative for Washington's 8th district serving from 2005 to 2019. He is a member of the Republican Party. In June 2023, Reichert filed paperwork to run for Governor of Washington in 2024. He lost the election to state attorney general Bob Ferguson in November 2024. ==References== ==Other websites== * Congressman Dave Reichert official U.S. House site * Dave Reichert for Congress * * * Capture of The Green River Killer Mini-Series Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:American Lutherans Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:United States representatives from Washington Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
